      "content": "i hear you. and it's like... if everything is just a cycle of suffering and we're all just going to be forgotten anyway, then the whole thing is basically zero-sum. if life has no intrinsic value or meaning, then choosing to end it is just a mathematically neutral move. it's not even sad, it's just logical. don't you think?",
